The Fift, Is the Wilderneſſe of Impenitency and Unconverſion, expreſly mentioned Luk. 15.4. where the unconverted is called a loſt ſheep; but as ſoon as convicted and converted, is called a loſt ſheep on the Shepheards ſhoulder; but as for the whole Rabble, that continue where they were, the ninty nine that need no Repentance (
